The purpose of joy2mat is to provide a matlab joystick interface using
pygame. In particular joy2mat was written to provide a matlab based
SpaceNavigator ( 3dConnexion ) interface for OSX. 

Dependencies:
  matlab2009 or higher
  python2.6 or higher
  pygame

Use:
  In a console:
  python joy2mat.py

  Then in matlab:
  j = joystick
  j.pull  # Returns a single joystick event struct
  j.pullall # Returns all of the current joystick events in a struct 

